Uses of Class
dto.UserDTO

  • Packages that use UserDTO 
    Package Description
    facades  

    • Uses of UserDTO in facades

      Methods in facades that return UserDTO 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      UserDTO UserFacade.createUser(String username, String password, String passwordCheck)
      createUser has the purpose of registering a user to the our database, and adds a "user" role by default, to the registered user.
      UserDTO UserFacade.deleteUser(String userName)
      deleteUser deletes the user that is specified from the userName, through our REST endpoint.
      UserDTO UserFacade.editUser(String username, String editedPassword)
      editUser has the purpose of editing a password in the database, to an user.
      Methods in facades that return types with arguments of type UserDTO 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      List<UserDTO> UserFacade.getAllUsers()
      getAllUsers simply has the purpose of retrieving all users from our database, And return the Username (UserDTO) in a List.
